<|startoftext|>Dish: vegan chocolate macaroni and cheese with cinnamon
Directions: preheat oven to 450f
in a medium bowl , cream together margarine and flour with the mixer until smooth , then add all the ingredients to the dough
let rise until it is soft-but not sticky
add the egg by spoonfuls at a time and mix after each addition
let rise until you reach room temperature
in a 1-cup measuring cup , whisk the egg with the milk and the cold water
fold the dough into the dough and roll into 2 balls with a rolling pin , at first in an even layer in a lightly greased greased pie plate but then starting to roll more tightly up the sides , to resemble chocolate doughnuts
cut into 1- 1 / 2 inch pieces , 2 times the size of the small cookies and make the top
remove each dough ball 2 paces to fill the bottom halfway
roll the dough into balls approximately twice the size of each cookie cookies , about 1 / 2 in wide
dont roll them out a lot at first , as this will make them a bit sticky
in a 6-quart muffinpan , heat the milk over a small heat until the brown sugar dissolves
when the mixture has cooled , stir until it is heated through
cover the dough balls with the sugar mixture and let them rise slightly in the prepared pie plate
let these rise longer until they are completely set on your pizza peel
when they are almost the same size , dip each round in butter slightly in the hot water a few times after dipping each of their cookies, coating them
now you have about four rolls per cookie , and they should be slightly sticky as they bake, but not dry
dip each cookie in the butter a few times and then brush them with the hot water , then spoon the flour mixture into the cracks and crevices in the dough , taking care not to burn them
in a 2-qt or bigger deep sauce pan , place all the ingredients
spoon the dough lightly over top , and mix well and evenly until you have a smooth dough
pour it into a baking dish , and bake in the oven for 35-40 minutes, checking once every 5-10 minutes to ensure they are dry and are not over baked
